{{Youth rights sidebar}} In various [[jurisdiction]]s, the '''gambling age''' is the minimum age which one can [[gambling|gamble]]. In some countries, gambling is illegal for all people regardless of age, so a minimum age does not exist. In other countries, there are different age limits for different types of gambling.
